  '2-1-1': { thai: "ในข้อให้เติมคำในช่องว่าง: \"heard a noise of breaking when one teenager threw a …\" บทความมีถ้อยคำที่ตรงกันคือ \"One of these young shepherds tossed a rock into an opening on the side of a cliff and was surpr…\" จึงคำตอบคือ \"rock\" (paraphrase จากข้อความใน passage)", para: "noise breaking teenager = shepherds tossed opening surprised = rock", exactHints: "rock|heard|noise|breaking|teenager", exact: "One of these young shepherds tossed a rock into an opening on the side of a cliff and was surprised to hear a shattering sound." },
  '2-1-2': { thai: "ในข้อให้เติมคำในช่องว่าง: \"teenagers went into the …\" บทความมีถ้อยคำที่ตรงกันคือ \"He and his companions later entered the cave and stumbled across a collection of large clay jar…\" จึงคำตอบคือ \"cave\" (paraphrase จากข้อความใน passage)", para: "teenagers = companions entered stumbled across = cave", exactHints: "cave|teenagers", exact: "He and his companions later entered the cave and stumbled across a collection of large clay jars, seven of which contained scrolls with writing on them." },
