  '2-1-4': { thai: "ในข้อให้เติมคำในช่องว่าง: \"thought to have been written by group of people known as the …\" บทความมีถ้อยคำที่ตรงกันคือ \"The area was known as Judea at that time, and the people are thought to have belonged to a grou…\" จึงคำตอบคือ \"Essenes\" (paraphrase จากข้อความใน passage)", para: "thought group known = thought belonged called devout = Essenes", exactHints: "essenes|thought|group|known", exact: "The area was known as Judea at that time, and the people are thought to have belonged to a group called the Essenes, a devout Jewish sect." },
