  '2-1-6': { thai: "ข้อความในข้อว่า \"The Bedouin teenagers who found the scrolls were disappointed by how little money they received for them.\" บทความไม่ได้ให้รายละเอียดเพียงพอที่จะยืนยันหรือปฏิเสธข้อนี้โดยตรง (อ้างอิงใกล้เคียง: \"In late 1946 or early 1947, three Bedouin teenagers were tending their goats and sheep near the…\") จึงตอบ NOT GIVEN", para: "bedouin teenagers found = bedouin teenagers tending ancient = NOT GIVEN", exactHints: "the bedouin|bedouin|teenagers|found|scrolls|disappointed|little", exact: "In late 1946 or early 1947, three Bedouin teenagers were tending their goats and sheep near the ancient settlement of Qumran, located on the northwest shore of the Dead Sea in what is now known as the West Bank." },
  '2-1-7': { thai: "ข้อความในข้อว่า \"There is agreement among academics about the origin of the Dead Sea Scrolls.\" ไม่ตรงกับบทความ เพราะบทความระบุว่า \"Along with biblical texts, the scrolls include documents about sectarian regulations and religi…\" ซึ่งขัดกับสิ่งที่ข้ออ้าง (หรือให้ข้อมูลตรงข้าม) จึงตอบ FALSE", para: "scrolls = biblical scrolls include documents = FALSE", exactHints: "there|dead sea scrolls|agreement|among|academics|origin|scrolls", exact: "Along with biblical texts, the scrolls include documents about sectarian regulations and religious writings that do not appear in the Old Testament." },
