  '4-1-3': { thai: "ข้อความในข้อว่า \"Ricardo Rocha has carried out studies of bats in different parts of the world.\" บทความไม่ได้ให้รายละเอียดเพียงพอที่จะยืนยันหรือปฏิเสธข้อนี้โดยตรง (อ้างอิงใกล้เคียง: \"Enter University of Cambridge zoologist Ricardo Rocha.\") จึงตอบ NOT GIVEN", para: "carried studies bats = university cambridge zoologist ricardo = NOT GIVEN", exactHints: "ricardo rocha|ricardo|rocha|carried|studies|different|parts", exact: "Enter University of Cambridge zoologist Ricardo Rocha." },
  '4-1-4': { thai: "ข้อความในข้อว่า \"Habitat modification has resulted in indigenous bats in Madagascar becoming useful to farmers.\" ตรงกับข้อมูลในบทความ เพราะบทความระบุว่า \"Co-leading an international team of scientists, Rocha found that several species of indigenous …\" ซึ่งยืนยันสิ่งที่ข้อกล่าวถึงได้ชัดเจน จึงตอบ TRUE", para: "habitat modification resulted = co-leading international scientists several = TRUE", exactHints: "habitat|madagascar|habitat|modification|resulted|indigenous|madagascar|becoming", exact: "Co-leading an international team of scientists, Rocha found that several species of indigenous bats are taking advantage of habitat modification to hunt insects swarming above the country's rice fields." },
  '4-1-5': { thai: "ข้อความในข้อว่า \"The Malagasy mouse-eared bat is more common than other indigenous bat species in Madagascar.\" บทความไม่ได้ให้รายละเอียดเพียงพอที่จะยืนยันหรือปฏิเสธข้อนี้โดยตรง (อ้างอิงใกล้เคียง: \"Rocha's new study shows that several species of bats are giving Madagascar's rice farmers a vit…\") จึงตอบ NOT GIVEN", para: "indigenous species madagascar = rocha's several species giving = NOT GIVEN", exactHints: "the malagasy|madagascar|malagasy|mouse-eared|common|indigenous|species|madagascar", exact: "Rocha's new study shows that several species of bats are giving Madagascar's rice farmers a vital pest control service by feasting on plagues of insects." },
  '4-1-6': { thai: "ข้อความในข้อว่า \"Bats may feed on paddy swarming caterpillars and grass webworms.\" ตรงกับข้อมูลในบทความ เพราะบทความระบุว่า \"‘We found that six species of bat are preying on rice pests, including the paddy swarming cater…\" ซึ่งยืนยันสิ่งที่ข้อกล่าวถึงได้ชัดเจน จึงตอบ TRUE", para: "paddy swarming caterpillars = species preying including swarming = TRUE", exactHints: "bats|paddy|swarming|caterpillars|grass|webworms", exact: "‘We found that six species of bat are preying on rice pests, including the paddy swarming caterpillar and grass webworm." },
  '4-1-7': { thai: "ในข้อให้เติมคำในช่องว่าง: \"DNA analysis of bat …\" บทความมีถ้อยคำที่ตรงกันคือ \"They next used DNA barcoding techniques to analyse droppings collected from bats at the differe…\" จึงคำตอบคือ \"droppings\" (paraphrase จากข้อความใน passage)", para: "analysis = barcoding techniques analyse collected = droppings", exactHints: "droppings|analysis", exact: "They next used DNA barcoding techniques to analyse droppings collected from bats at the different sites." },
  '4-1-8': { thai: "ในข้อให้เติมคำในช่องว่าง: \"ate pests of rice, …\" บทความมีถ้อยคำที่ตรงกันคือ \"so found indications that the bats were consuming pests of other crops, including the black twi…\" จึงคำตอบคือ \"coffee\" (paraphrase จากข้อความใน passage)", para: "pests = indications consuming including infests = coffee", exactHints: "coffee|pests", exact: "so found indications that the bats were consuming pests of other crops, including the black twig borer (which infests coffee plants), the sugarcane cicada, the macadamia nut-borer, and the sober tabby (a pest of citrus fruits)." },
  '4-1-9': { thai: "ในข้อให้เติมคำในช่องว่าง: \"prevent the spread of disease by eating …\" บทความมีถ้อยคำที่ตรงกันคือ \"ile the animal is often associated with spreading disease, Rocha and his team found evidence th…\" จึงคำตอบคือ \"mosquitoes\" (paraphrase จากข้อความใน passage)", para: "prevent spread disease = animal associated spreading disease = mosquitoes", exactHints: "mosquitoes|prevent|spread|disease|eating", exact: "ile the animal is often associated with spreading disease, Rocha and his team found evidence that Malagasy bats feed not just on crop pests but also on mosquitoes — carriers of malaria, Rift Valley fever virus and elephantiasis — as well as" },
