  '4-1-11': { thai: "ในข้อให้เติมคำในช่องว่าง: \"the buildings where they roost become …\" บทความมีถ้อยคำที่ตรงกันคือ \"And as well as roosting in trees, the bats sometimes roost in buildings, but are not welcomed t…\" จึงคำตอบคือ \"unclean\" (paraphrase จากข้อความใน passage)", para: "buildings roost become = roosting sometimes buildings welcomed = unclean", exactHints: "unclean|buildings|roost|become", exact: "And as well as roosting in trees, the bats sometimes roost in buildings, but are not welcomed there because they make them unclean." },
