  '4-1-13': { thai: "ในข้อให้เติมคำในช่องว่าง: \"farmers should provide special …\" บทความมีถ้อยคำที่ตรงกันคือ \"Rocha says, ‘With the right help, we hope that farmers can promote this mutually beneficial rel…\" จึงคำตอบคือ \"houses\" (paraphrase จากข้อความใน passage)", para: "farmers should provide = farmers promote mutually beneficial = houses", exactHints: "houses|farmers|should|provide|special", exact: "Rocha says, ‘With the right help, we hope that farmers can promote this mutually beneficial relationship by installing bat houses.’ Rocha and his colleagues believe that maximising bat populations can help to boost crop yields and promote s" },
  '4-2-14': { thai: "ย่อหน้า E มีเนื้อหาที่ตรงกับหัวข้อในข้อมากที่สุด (An explanation of the need for research to focus on individuals with a fairly consistent income) โดยเฉพาะประโยค \"According to Ogilvie, the database provides multiple indicators for the same individuals, makin…\" จึงเลือก E", para: "explanation need research = according ogilvie database provides = E", exactHints: "e|an|explanation|research|focus|individuals", exact: "According to Ogilvie, the database provides multiple indicators for the same individuals, making it possible to analyse links between literacy, numeracy, wealth, and industriousness, for individual women and men over the long term." },
