  '4-2-19': { thai: "ในข้อ: \"The database sheds light on the lives of individuals, as well as those of their ___\" หลักฐานในบทความคือ \"‘We can follow the same people — and their descendants — across 300 years of educational and ec…\" จึงตอบ descendants", para: "database sheds light = follow across educational economic = descendants", exactHints: "descendants|the|database|sheds|light|lives", exact: "‘We can follow the same people — and their descendants — across 300 years of educational and economic change,’ she says." },
  '4-2-20': { thai: "ในข้อ: \"Ana Regina and Magdalena were reprimanded for reading while they should have been paying attention to a ___\" หลักฐานในบทความคือ \"Stories like that of the 24-year-olds Ana Regina and Magdalena Riethmüllerin, who were chastise…\" จึงตอบ sermon", para: "regina magdalena reprimanded = stories 24-year-olds regina magdalena = sermon", exactHints: "sermon|ana regina|magdalena|regina|magdalena|reprimanded|should", exact: "Stories like that of the 24-year-olds Ana Regina and Magdalena Riethmüllerin, who were chastised in 1707 for reading books in church instead of listening to the sermon." },
  '4-2-21': { thai: "ในข้อ: \"As a punishment, Juliana Schweickherdt was later given a ___\" หลักฐานในบทความคือ \"When Juliana continued taking jobs reserved for male guild members, she was summoned before the…\" จึงตอบ fine", para: "punishment juliana schweickherdt = juliana continued taking reserved = fine", exactHints: "fine|as|juliana schweickherdt|punishment|juliana|schweickherdt|later", exact: "When Juliana continued taking jobs reserved for male guild members, she was summoned before the guild court and told to pay a fine equivalent to one third of a servant's annual wage." },
  '4-2-22': { thai: "ในข้อ: \"Cases like this illustrate how the guilds could prevent ___ and stop skilled people from working\" หลักฐานในบทความคือ \"The dominance of guilds not only prevented people from using their skills, but also held back e…\" จึงตอบ innovation", para: "cases illustrate guilds = dominance guilds prevented skills = innovation", exactHints: "innovation|cases|cases|illustrate|guilds|prevent", exact: "The dominance of guilds not only prevented people from using their skills, but also held back even the simplest industrial innovation." },
  '4-2-23': { thai: "ย่อหน้า B มีเนื้อหาที่ตรงกับหัวข้อในข้อมากที่สุด (Which TWO statements does the writer make about literacy rates in Section B?) โดยเฉพาะประโยค \"During this period, Germany and Scandinavia had excellent literacy rates, but their economies g…\" จึงเลือก B", para: "literacy rates section = period germany scandinavia excellent = B", exactHints: "literacy|rates|section|which|section", exact: "During this period, Germany and Scandinavia had excellent literacy rates, but their economies grew slowly and they industrialised late." },
